content:
Suppose there is a basket with an unknown number of apples. If the basket had 8 more apples added to it, the number of apples increased by 200%. If there are currently 18 apples in the basket, what was the original number of apples in the basket? 
[JSON data]: {"current_number_of_apples": 18, "percent_increase": 200, "added_apples": 8} 
[JSON data] code: 
{
    "current_number_of_apples": 18,
    "percent_increase": 200,
    "added_apples": 8
}
